「YesterWeather」 is a unique weather application that focuses on comparing the weather conditions of yesterday and today, so that you can be fully prepared every day before going out!

-Provided by 「YesterWeather」-
[Simple interface] Only show the important weather information of yesterday and today, as well as the comparison result;
[Widgets] Grabbing today's weather condition without opening the app;
[Handy Interaction] Automatically update weather information every hour, what you see is real time;
[Bilingual support] Support Chinese and English according to the system language setting;
[Global Weather] Covering 3240 cities, counties and districts in China and 150,000 cities worldwide;

-More by 「YesterWeather」-
This is a special and interesting independently developed application that will have more useful features and functionalities incrementally and iteratively in the future.

